markdownRemark.html:
You can use this file as a template for creating a post.

Path

Try to use a descriptive and unique path, usually the post's title should do. Make sure to use a valid URL.

Example:

title: "Ten reasons why pizza is my favourite food"
path: "/posts/ten-reasons-why-pizza-is-my-favourite-food"
